ActCustoms Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Proof of Origin of Imported Goods Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the PROOF OF ORIGIN OF IMPORTED GOODS REGULATIONS in order to incorporate the Canada-European Free Trade Association Free Trade Agreement, the Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement and the Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement into Canada's existing regulatory framework by allowing customs procedures related to proof of origin to be administered in accordance with the terms of each of these Free Trade Agreements.
